00:59:57,640 --> 01:00:00,120
<i>On the day I meet you,</i>

769
01:00:01,500 --> 01:00:04,380
<i>I hope the winds blow.</i>

770
01:00:08,380 --> 01:00:11,320
<i>So that my longing would reach you</i>

771
01:00:12,820 --> 01:00:14,970
<i>and create a path.</i>

772
01:00:44,070 --> 01:00:45,960
Yeong Eun.

773
01:00:48,030 --> 01:00:49,980
Jae Gook.

774
01:01:00,170 --> 01:01:01,980
Yeong Eun.

775
01:01:06,420 --> 01:01:08,700
Say hello. This is photographer Yoon Jae Gook.

776
01:01:08,700 --> 01:01:12,000
Oh, hello.

777
01:01:12,000 --> 01:01:13,120
Hello.

778
01:01:13,120 --> 01:01:17,470
I am Kim Soo Min, the one in charge of planning this fashion week.

779
01:01:17,470 --> 01:01:20,270
You'll be going to the party later, right?

780
01:01:20,270 --> 01:01:22,270
Do you want to go with me? I'll drive.

781
01:01:22,270 --> 01:01:23,960
Sure.

782
01:01:25,040 --> 01:01:27,200
Honey!

783
01:01:28,920 --> 01:01:29,990
I'll see you later.

784
01:01:29,990 --> 01:01:31,440
Okay.

785
01:01:43,910 --> 01:01:46,450
Have you been well?

786
01:01:48,700 --> 01:01:50,240
Yes.

787
01:01:51,790 --> 01:01:54,460
I saw your exhibition

788
01:01:54,460 --> 01:01:57,160
through pictures in a magazine.

789
01:02:02,330 --> 01:02:04,620
But it was still admirable.

790
01:02:06,170 --> 01:02:08,200
How are you these days?

791
01:02:15,260 --> 01:02:18,760
<i>Team Leader... I mean, CEO.</i>

792
01:02:18,760 --> 01:02:20,920
<i>By the way, what is the name of our brand?</i>

793
01:02:20,920 --> 01:02:24,560
<i>Well, how about I come up with one as the chief?</i>

794
01:02:24,560 --> 01:02:26,220
<i>We have a name.</i>

795
01:02:26,220 --> 01:02:28,020
<i>What is it?</i>

796
01:02:32,300 --> 01:02:34,710
<i>[Hwa-dap]</i>

797
01:02:34,710 --> 01:02:38,400
<i>Hwa? What does it mean?</i>

798
01:02:38,400 --> 01:02:40,740
<i>Hwa-dap (response).</i>

799
01:02:40,740 --> 01:02:44,930
<i> The promises I made with you. Your love has made a path.</i>

800
01:02:44,930 --> 01:02:47,990
To the new designers who were invited to the sideshow, please come this way!

801
01:02:47,990 --> 01:02:49,630
Okay!

802
01:02:51,060 --> 01:02:54,580
<i>Walking down that path</i>

803
01:02:54,580 --> 01:02:59,090
<i>is my response.</i>

804
01:02:59,090 --> 01:03:02,310
How are you these days?

805
01:03:02,310 --> 01:03:10,390
♫ <i>I let out a long sigh and just stare blankly at the sky</i> ♫

806
01:03:10,390 --> 01:03:13,390
♫ <i>Already charred black</i> ♫

807
01:03:13,390 --> 01:03:17,120
<i>And like that,</i>

808
01:03:17,120 --> 01:03:20,820
<i>now,</i>

809
01:03:20,820 --> 01:03:23,170
<i>we are breaking up.</i>

810
01:03:23,170 --> 01:03:26,690
♫ <i>I miss you</i> ♫

811
01:03:26,690 --> 01:03:33,630
♫ <i>Both the season of youth and the warm wind</i> ♫

812
01:03:33,630 --> 01:03:39,120
♫ <i>Don't mean anything</i> ♫

813
01:03:39,120 --> 01:03:42,690
♫ <i>Because you're not here</i> ♫

814
01:03:42,690 --> 01:03:46,690
♫ <i>To clear my head</i> ♫

815
01:03:46,690 --> 01:03:53,700
♫ <i>When I keep aimlessly wandering the streets</i> ♫

816
01:03:53,700 --> 01:04:02,390
♫ <i>Without being aware, I'm here in front of your house</i> ♫

817
01:04:02,390 --> 01:04:07,710
♫ <i>At first, I was calmer than I thought I would be</i> ♫

818
01:04:07,710 --> 01:04:13,980
♫ <i>The longing hurts more than breaking up</i> ♫

819
01:04:13,980 --> 01:04:18,790
♫ <i>It is just a day to endure</i> ♫

820
01:04:18,790 --> 01:04:22,070
♫ <i>The more time passes, the more it intensifies</i> ♫

821
01:04:22,070 --> 01:04:31,450
♫ <i>Love leaves. Why does only the farewell remain?</i> ♫

822
01:04:31,450 --> 01:04:38,210
♫ <i>Even still, I, who am truly like a fool</i> ♫

823
01:04:38,210 --> 01:04:43,790
♫ <i>Survive like this</i> ♫

824
01:04:43,790 --> 01:04:49,980
♫ <i>Turning away again</i> ♫

825
01:04:51,830 --> 01:04:55,180
♫ <i>My departing footsteps are heavy</i> ♫

826
01:04:57,140 --> 01:04:59,120
<i>[Thank you for watching Now, We Are Breaking Up]</i>
